[{'text': '&lt;P&gt;PROBLEM TO BE SOLVED: To provide an image forming device having simple and inexpensive construction for preventing the skewing of envelopes.  &lt;P&gt;SOLUTION: A recording sheet carrying mechanism 3 consists of a pick roller 10 for delivering recording sheets P placed on a feed tray 2 to the inside of a device body, a recording sheet guide member 11 for guiding the front ends of the delivered recording sheets P, a feed roller 12 for further delivering the recording sheets P to the side of an image forming part, and a thrust roller 29 for thrusting the recording sheets P against the feed roller 12. A recording sheet guide face 37 of the recording sheet guide member 11 is arranged on the side of the feed roller 12 beyond an abutting face between the feed roller 12 and the thrust roller 29 and a gap (t) is formed between a first small diameter portion 26 of the feed roller 12 and a second small diameter portion 33 of the thrust roller 29, thus avoiding the abutment of an envelope end region 38 on the feed roller 12 and the thrust roller 29.  &lt;P&gt;COPYRIGHT: (C)2007,JPO&amp;INPIT', 'language': 'en', 'truncated': False}
